snippet.title: I, the Inquisitor - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
“I, the Inquisitor” is a dark, action-adventure game that takes place in an alternative version of history where Jesus did not die on the cross but came down and unleashed fury on all nonbelievers. 1500 years later, an army of Inquisitors brutally enforce the faith. You are one of them!

Add to wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1880470/I_the_Inquisitor/
Join the official Discord server: https://discord.gg/uexaVXqwrh
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ItheInquisitor 
Follow on Facebook: https://facebook.com/ItheInquisitor 

More information: http://itheinquisitor.game
